| **H2 (Coherence Differences)** | ‚úÖ **SUPPORTED** | The MC-SCI scores successfully differentiated the speakers. McCain's institutional speech (0.048) exhibited lower character tension (higher coherence) than Sanders' populist critique (0.073), aligning with the hypothesis. |
